Bootstrap: docker
From: python:3.12-slim

%labels
    Author wel24kif
    Version 2.9
    Description vcf2phylip — VCF to PHYLIP/FASTA converter for diploid organisms
    Source https://github.com/edgardomortiz/vcf2phylip

%post
    apt-get update && apt-get install -y git && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
    git clone https://github.com/edgardomortiz/vcf2phylip.git /opt/vcf2phylip
    chmod +x /opt/vcf2phylip/vcf2phylip.py
    ln -s /opt/vcf2phylip/vcf2phylip.py /usr/local/bin/vcf2phylip

%test
    vcf2phylip --help

%help
    vcf2phylip 2.8 — convert multi-sample VCF to PHYLIP or FASTA alignment.
    Handles diploid GATK VCFs: hets encoded as IUPAC ambiguity codes by default.

    Usage (FASTA output):
        vcf2phylip --input samples.vcf --fasta --output-prefix output
